==Useful Info==
'''Servants of whispers''' are fragile but formidable support casters often found roaming the [[Desolation of Salt]] with a band of [[saltling]]s and in Desolation-exclusive ruins with [[imperial myrmidon]]s, [[ragged hierophant]]s, [[ironbound convoker]]s and [[halazid warlock]]s. Their [[Still Winds]] invocation clears the ever present salt clouds, stripping away the player's concealment, and removes hazardous [[clouds]] covering allies, shutting down spells such as [[Freezing Cloud]] and [[Ring of Flames]] and lessening the effects of spells like [[Glaciate]] and [[Fire Storm]]. Occasionally, they will cast a special invocation version of [[Lightning Bolt]], dealing significant [[electricity]] damage to [[Electricity#Electricity Resistance|uninsulated]] players.

